    <h1>Manual Action</h1>
    <p class="description">A penalty applied by Google's human spam team when a site violates webmaster guidelines. Unlike algorithm updates, <strong>manual actions appear in Search Console</strong> and require a formal reconsideration request to lift.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
